Assigning Addresses to VLAN Interfaces

nmcli con add type vlan con-name VLAN20 dev enp1s0 id 20 ip4 10.10.10.10/24 \
gw4 10.10.10.254

nmcli con add type vlan con-name VLAN30 dev enp1s0 id 30

